OL,3,CTeenagers sentenced for shooting after
OL,4,Ctrying to flee the country
OL,6,FTwo teenagers have been sentenced for
OL,7,Fa shooting in Nottingham city centre
OL,8,Fafter trying to flee the country.
OL,10,FThey appeared at Nottingham Crown
OL,11,FCourt on Friday (24 January) and were
OL,12,Fsentenced to a combined 23 and a half
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FThey both pleaded guilty possession of
OL,16,Fa firearm with intent to endanger life.
