OL,3,CTeenagers sentenced for shooting after
OL,4,Ctrying to flee the country
OL,6,FRamarni Spencer and Pharrell McLennon
OL,7,Fboth fired shots at another youth as
OL,8,Fthey rode an electric bike through the
OL,9,FBridgeway Centre, The Meadows,
OL,10,FNottingham, on 5 May 2024.
OL,12,FPolice believe that no one was injured
OL,13,Fin the attack.
OL,15,FAfter the shooting they booked tickets
OL,16,Fon a flight to Alicante, Spain.
OL,18,FThe pair, now 18, were arrested at the
OL,19,Fdeparture lounge of East Midlands
OL,20,FAirport as they ordered burgers.
