OL,6,FMcLennon, of Maypole, Clifton,
OL,7,Freceived an extended sentence of 13
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FThe first ten years will be spent in
OL,11,Fcustody, while he will then remain on
OL,12,Flicence for the final three years of
OL,13,Fhis sentence.
OL,15,FSpencer, of Marlborough Road, Beeston,
OL,16,Freceived an extended sentence of ten-
OL,17,Fand-a-half years.
