OL,6,FThe first seven-and-a-half years will
OL,7,Fbe served in custody, while he will
OL,8,Fthen remain on licence for the final
OL,9,Fthree years of his sentence.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Chris Berryman, of
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,14,F"Thankfully, we do not believe anyone
OL,15,Fwas seriously injured during this
OL,16,Fincident but that is no thanks to
OL,17,Fthese two teenagers.
