OL,6,F"The incident took place at a busy
OL,7,Fshopping precinct on a spring
OL,8,Fafternoon. Terrified onlookers sought
OL,9,Frefuge in shops and Spencer and
OL,10,FMcLennon showed absolutely no concern
OL,11,Ffor their safety whatsoever.
OL,13,F"The weapons were not recovered so I
OL,14,Fwould urge anyone with any information
OL,15,Fabout their whereabouts to get in
OL,16,Ftouch with police.
